Emerson Arcadia 2001 (1982)



8-bit Console system



Features:

---------


* CPU: Signetics 2650A 3.58 MHz


* Co-Processor: Signetics 2637UVI (audio & video processing unit)


* RAM: 1024 bytes


* 128x208 in 8 colors


* 4 8x8 single color sprites


* single channel sound


