Telenova Compis (1985)



Features:

---------


* CPU: Intel 80186 8 MHz


* Co-Processor: 82720 (Graphic), 8087(arithmetic coprocessor),


* RAM: 128 kb or 256 kb, expandable to 768 kb


* ROM: Unknown


* Text Modes: 50 x 25, 80 x 25


