$info=prav8d
$bio
Pravetz 8D (1985)



Features:

---------


* CPU: CM630 - Bulgarian copy of the 6502 1 MHz


* RAM: 48 KB


* ROM: 16 KB


* Text Modes: 40 columns x 28 lines


* Graphic Modes: 240 x 200 (+ 3 text lines)


